snippet.title: High Energy Heroes [高能英雄] Game Trailer
snippet.description: High Energy Heroes is developed by Tencent, rumors have it that it is a mobile game created by replacing skins from Apex Legends mobile game. The game has switched to a 4-player team mode, and the character skins are more in line with Asian aesthetics.
